      "role": "user",
      "content": "i’ve been feeling this intense connection to things i never learned, like this deep cellular recognition of patterns and old environments... i’m starting to realize it’s not just intuition, it’s literally written in my dna. like my body is trying to trigger a memory that isn't conscious yet. do you know anything about how to use meditation to actually unlock those genetic sequences?",
